version_description: This  version is with capo on second fret and it is like the original version by " The Dubliners"
Changed some misplaced and incorrect chords.
I've tried to make this sound exactly how the Dubliners sang it in the original version. its sounds pretty close to me, plus its very easy to play since its pretty standard chords.
Easy to read version of this classic Dubliners song.

This version is in the same key as the original song and it includes the chords throughout the entire tab. This version contains chords that match the ones played in the original song, and at the time of submitting this, is the only version with chords to do so.
